text: Rachael May Taylor (born 11 July 1984) is an Australian actress and model. She acts in both Australian and Hollywood movies. She played Maggie Madsen in the 2007 movie Transformers. She played Teri in Man-Thing. Taylor was born in Launceston, Tasmania. ==References== Category:Australian television actors Category:Australian movie actors Category:Australian models Category:1984 births Category:Living people
